---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { site } from "../data/site";
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`Experience | ${site.name}`}
  description={`Professional experience of ${site.name} in embedded systems, Embedded Linux, Edge AI, and hardware/software integration.`}
>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="section intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">Experience</p>
      <h1>Building embedded systems for real products and industrial environments.</h1>

      <p class="lead">
        My experience combines embedded software development, hardware/software
        integration, Linux-based device platforms, industrial systems, communication
        modules, and technical leadership.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="timeline">
      <article class="card item">
        <p class="date">Current Focus</p>
        <h2>Senior Embedded Software Engineer / Technical Lead</h2>
        <p>
          Leading and contributing to embedded systems projects involving Embedded
          Linux, Qt HMI, device networking, backend services, industrial IO,
          payment and communication integration, and production-oriented system design.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card item">
        <p class="date">Embedded Linux and Device Platforms</p>
        <h2>Linux-Based Product Development</h2>
        <p>
          Designed and integrated Linux-based embedded platforms for industrial and
          communication devices, including local HMI, system services, networking,
          configuration interfaces, and device-level behavior.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card item">
        <p class="date">Firmware and Hardware Integration</p>
        <h2>Low-Level Embedded Development</h2>
        <p>
          Developed firmware and integrated hardware interfaces for embedded products,
          including cellular modules, IO handling, sensors, communication protocols,
          hardware bring-up, and field debugging.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card item">
        <p class="date">Industrial and Communication Systems</p>
        <h2>Product-Level System Integration</h2>
        <p>
          Worked on systems such as vending machines, conference and voting platforms,
          GSM/GNSS dataloggers, diesel generator controllers, and video communication
          systems with a focus on reliability, integration, and practical operation.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card item">
        <p class="date">Technical Direction</p>
        <h2>Architecture, Debugging, and Delivery</h2>
        <p>
          Experienced in breaking down complex product requirements, reviewing system
          risks, coordinating embedded hardware and software tasks, debugging across
          multiple layers, and preparing systems for real-world use.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .eyebrow {
    color: #67e8f9;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 72px);
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .lead {
    max-width: 820px;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .timeline {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .date {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    color: #67e8f9;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #93c5fd;
  }

  p {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
